
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-korhonen-netlmm-lma-discovery-01.txt'>
    <title>"LMA Discovery for Proxy Mobile IPv6", Jouni Korhonen, Vijay Devarapalli</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-korhonen-netlmm-lma-discovery-01.txt</link>
    <description>Large Proxy Mobile IPv6 deployments would benefit from a functionality, where a Mobile Access Gateway could dynamically discover a Local Mobility Anchor for a Mobile Node attaching to a Proxy Mobile IPv6 domain.  The purpose of the dynamic discovery functionality is to reduce the amount of static configuration in the Mobile Access Gateway.  This specification describes a number of possible dynamic Local Mobility Anchor discovery solutions.</description>
    <dc:date>2009-02-23T23:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
